channel.title: What do these mean?
channel.description:
When I add portals or objects and make them give xp, or make them tele you places, what does this mean. I found it in other cases.

What's absX, and absY? I know object X and Object Y are the (x,y) coords of the object.
H E L P I S A P P R E C I A T E D !!! :)
